reviewText: I was expecting more softball and beer...
Enjoyed it. Very good independent film. Music was very good also. Kelsey Thomas was shooting star! Try it out, you will like it.

This review probably isn't going to help you much because I show up in the film as a mascot duck and am therefore extremely biased, but Summer League is a lovely little film you should add to your collection if you like the following: softball, Austin Texas, families, love, extremely fast waiters and parody Hulk Hogan t-shirts.

Plus, the duck is pretty cool.  Order this, love it and show it to everybody you know.
